data.description:
This is a great, newly remodeled home on the golf course in Eagle. There are new tile floors, new carpet, new slab granite in kitchen and master bath and new interior paint. 

Neighborhood Description

This is a wonderful neighborhood in Eagle that surrounds a beautiful golf course. It offers convenient access to schools, shopping and downtown Boise.
data.whatILove: You will love the spectacular kitchen with view of golf course!
